## 8. Reporting and Escalation

### 8.1 Ethics Concern Reporting

Staff can report AI ethics concerns through:
- Direct report to AI Governance Contact ({{ ai_governance_contact | default("to be appointed", true) }})
- Incident reporting channel (as defined in the AI Incident Response Plan)
- Anonymous reporting (if available)

### 8.2 Escalation Matrix

| Issue Severity | Escalated To | Response Time |
|---|---|---|
| Low (e.g., minor output quality) | Tool Owner | 5 business days |
| Medium (e.g., suspected bias) | AI Governance Contact | 2 business days |
| High (e.g., discriminatory outcome) | Senior Management | 24 hours |
| Critical (e.g., harm to individual) | CEO + Legal | Immediate |

